flowchart LR
    Failure["Failure event"] --> Classify["Classify failure mode"]
    Classify -->|Transient| Retry["Retry\nwait and run the same input again"]
    Classify -->|Reasoning| Reflect["Reflect\nfeed back what was wrong, why, and how to change"]
    Classify -->|Deterministic| Escalate["Escalate or stop\nproblem will not improve by repeating"]

    Retry --> Fast["Good for timeout, network, rate limit"]
    Reflect --> Better["Good for wrong arguments,\nformat violations, policy failures"]

    style Classify fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#7b1fa2
    style Retry fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1976d2
    style Reflect fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#388e3c
    style Escalate fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#f9a825
